  "2026-07-13T17:50:53.992Z",maintainer-agent,"Scope note from pm-4k6b directed pass 2026-07-13: (a) this item additionally owns the per-workspace graduation of algorithm (21)'s shrinkage pseudo-counts k (same label machinery as the (3)/(19) weight graduation). (b) Hard prerequisite recorded here because it must ship WITH the feedback loop: context/next envelopes must LOG the disclosed profile, per-item rank, and inclusion decision (propensity logging) so any future online/off-policy weight learning stays possible — an online contextual-bandit learner was considered on pm-4k6b 2026-07-13 and REJECTED as a separate algorithm precisely because it is this item's graduation territory; without propensity logs that door closes silently."
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
